messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Hello. Yes am looking for prayers.
Welcome! We're here to support you. What specific prayers are you looking for? Are there particular struggles or needs you'd like us to pray about?
Yes. I need to break the spirit of just over my life.

I understand, and I'm here to help you with that. Here's a powerful prayer to help break the spirit of lust:

---

Heavenly Father,  
We come before your throne room today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We come boldly and with confidence. We are praying against the Spirit of lust within our hearts, minds, and bodies. We renounce all sexual sins that we have been involved in the past, including fornication, masturbation, and pornography. In the name of Jesus Christ, we break all curses of lust and command all spirits of lust and perversion to come out now. We present our bodies to You as a living sacrifice and ask for Your strength to walk in sexual purity. We receive the Spirit of holiness in our lives now. Lord, we loosen ourselves from the Spirit of this world and overcome through the power of the Holy Spirit. We thank You for Your healing and deliverance. In Jesus' name, Amen.

---

Feel free to reach out if you need further support or guidance!
Thank you.
You're welcome! If you have any more requests or need further assistance, feel free to ask. We're here to support you on your journey. God bless!
I need deliverance.

I understand that you're seeking deliverance. Here's a prayer for deliverance that you can use:

---

Heavenly Father,  
We come before your throne today through the blood of Jesus Christ. We pray against the Spirit of lust and all other sexual sins that may be connected to it. We break all ungodly soul ties and command all spirits of loneliness and perversion to come out now. We take authority over our thoughts and bind all spirits of fantasy and lustful thinking. We cast out all spirits of perversion and receive the Spirit of holiness in our lives to walk in sexual purity. Lord, we ask for Your strength and guidance as we seek deliverance from these struggles. In the name of Jesus Christ, we declare freedom and healing. Amen.

---

If you need more support or specific resources, just let me know!
Thank you for this prayer. I should just pray it over and over again?

Yes, praying this prayer repeatedly can be a powerful way to reinforce your commitment to seeking deliverance and healing. It's also important to pray with faith and sincerity, trusting in God's power to bring about change in your life. Additionally, you may want to spend time in worship, reading scripture, and seeking support from others in the community. If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!
Okay.
If you have any more questions or need further support, just let me know. I'm here to help!
I will ask for help. Thank you for being here.
You're very welcome! It's great to hear that you're reaching out for help. Remember, you're not alone in this journey. If you need anything else or just want to talk, I'm here for you. God bless!
God bless you too.
Thank you! If you need anything else or have more questions in the future, don't hesitate to reach out. Take care and stay strong!
Yes I will.
